# Normalize text files to LF on checkin so Windows tools/editors can't
# silently flip line endings for the whole repo again. This was the root
# cause of a 1,300+ file "false diff" cleaned up in July 2026.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary types (never touch line endings in these)
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.pdf binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary

# .bat/.ps1 are already stored LF-only in this repo and run fine that way
# via Windows Task Scheduler / cmd.exe / PowerShell, so no override needed
# here — they fall under the default `* text=auto eol=lf` rule above.
